Tao's summary:

#include <deque> 
deque<int> gquiz; 
gquiz.push_back(10); 
gquiz.push_front(20); 
ngquiz.front();
ngquiz.back();
ngquiz.pop_front();
ngquiz.pop_back();
ngquiz.clear();
ngquiz.erase();

1. dequename.erase(position)
2. dequename.erase(startingposition, endingposition)

Examples:

Input: mydeque{1, 2, 3, 4, 5}, pos= 2
mydeque.erase(pos);
Output : 1, 2, 4, 5

Input: mydeque{1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8}, pos1= 3, pos2= 6
mydeque.erase(pos1, pos2);
Output : 1, 2, 3, 8

